                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAPREDUCE-1664&quot; title=&quot;Job Acls affect Queue Acls&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MAPREDUCE-1664&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MAPREDUCE-1664&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; changes the behavior of queue acls and job acls. This needs documentation changes to cluster_setup.xml and a small change in AccessControlList.java&lt;/p&gt;</description>
